  "Disarming Shot": {
    rank: 2,
    type: "Combat",
    approach: "Precision",
    skill: "Firearms",
    flavor: "Shooting a weapon out of someone's hand is, by any reasonable assessment, an extremely difficult shot. The angle, the timing, the margin for error, most marksmen will never attempt it. The ones who do either miss entirely or make it look easy.",
    description: """
      <h3>Activation:</h3>
      <p>As an Attack action using a readied ranged weapon, you may make a <strong>TN 4 Firearms (Precision)</strong> check targeting one character within the weapon's range.</p>
