      <p>If you succeed, your target suffers physical damage equal to your Precision, plus additional damage equal to your bonus successes. Choose one of your target's readied weapons; the target must resist with a <strong>TN 4 Conditioning check (Swiftness 2, Precision 5)</strong> or lose control of the chosen weapon, which travels 2 range bands in a direction of your choice.</p>
    """
  },
  "Wrest Control": {
