  Strike: {
    rank: 1,
    type: "Electronic Warfare",
    approach: null,
    skill: "Computers",
    flavor: "Disrupting someone's gear is a nuisance. Striking the operator behind it is a statement. A targeted burst of hostile code bypasses the hardware entirely and hits the person running it: frying feedback loops, spiking neural buffers, turning a rival hacker's own interface into a weapon against them.",
    description: """
      <h3>Activation:</h3>
      <p>As an Attack action, make a <strong>Computers check</strong> at the network's TN, targeting one character or sentry on your current node.</p>
