      <ul>
        <li><strong>(op)(op):</strong> The sentry is immediately fragged regardless of remaining Integrity.</li>
      </ul>
    """
  },
  "Puppet String": {
    rank: 2,
    type: "Electronic Warfare",
    approach: "Swiftness",
    skill: "Computers",
    flavor: "There are things you can do to a T-Doll that have no equivalent in human warfare. Seizing motor control is one of them. It is efficient, tactically sound, and deeply violating. Most operators who have seen it done to an ally never forget the look on their face.",
    description: """
      <h3>Activation:</h3>
      <p>As a Scheme action, make a <strong>Computers [Swiftness] check</strong> at the target's Security Rating.</p>
