    type: "Combat",
    approach: "Swiftness",
    skill: "Firearms",
    flavor: "Combat doctrine favors placing pieces on the board where they'll be most effective, but rarely does reality play out like a game. A marksman who can adapt to less-than-ideal conditions and still put rounds on target is a valuable asset to any team.",
